init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As the world begins to change, the survivors discover that the power of Mana is returning.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The survivors are able to use the power of Mana to fight back against the aliens and their minions.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the end the survivors decide to keep the power of Mana and stay small in numbers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are able to do anything they want and live in a world of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens launch a full scale attack and the humans are forced to go on the defensive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans are able to hold off the aliens for a while but the aliens are too powerful.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the humans are small in numbers and the aliens are able to overpower them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are able to take over the world of magic and the humans are forced to live in a world without magic.
